麦当娜向已故的兄弟克里斯托弗表示敬意：“长期以来，他是我最亲近的人” https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-tribute-late-brother-christopher-closest- human-to-me-for-so-long-3799996?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=madonna-tribute-已故的克里斯托弗兄弟长期以来一直是我最亲近的人Max PilleySun, 06 Oct 2024 21:24:17 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3799996 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>比麦当娜小两岁的克里斯托弗·西科尼 (Christopher Ciccone) 于周五（10 月 4 日）去世，享年 63 岁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-tribute-late-brother-christopher-closest-human-to-me-for-so-long-3799996">麦当娜向已故弟弟克里斯托弗致敬：“这么长时间以来，他是我最亲近的人”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/madonna_christopher_ciccone-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>向她去世、享年 63 岁的弟弟克里斯托弗·西科内 (Christopher Ciccone) 致以衷心的敬意。</p><p>他去世的消息得到了家人代表的证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonnas-brother-christopher-ciccone-dies-aged-63-3799975">他们透露，他于周五（10 月 4 日）在密歇根州因癌症去世</a>。</p><p>这位比克里斯托弗大两岁的流行偶像在她的 Instagram 帐户上发布了一条感人的个人信息，揭示了他们在成长过程中以及早期职业生涯中的亲密关系。</p><p>在他们两人多年来在一起的一系列照片旁边，她写道：“我的兄弟克里斯托弗去世了。这么长时间以来，他是我最亲近的人。很难解释我们之间的联系，但它源于一种理解，即我们与众不同，如果我们不遵循现状，社会将会给我们带来困难。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAy1hZpSqqd/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(